      {"type":"info","title":"Числа 70-99","markdown":"## 70-99: Сложная система\n\n### 70-79:\n71 = soixante et onze\n72 = soixante-douze\n73 = soixante-treize\n...\n79 = soixante-dix-neuf\n\n### 80-89:\n80 = quatre-vingts (с -s!)\n81 = quatre-vingt-un (без -s!)\n82 = quatre-vingt-deux\n...\n89 = quatre-vingt-neuf\n\n### 90-99:\n90 = quatre-vingt-dix\n91 = quatre-vingt-onze\n92 = quatre-vingt-douze\n...\n99 = quatre-vingt-dix-neuf\n\n### Правило -s:\nquatre-vingt**s** (80) теряет -s, когда после него идёт число."},
      {"type":"quiz","question":"Как по-французски 91?","options":[{"id":"a","text":"quatre-vingt-onze","correct":True},{"id":"b","text":"nonante-un","correct":False},{"id":"c","text":"quatre-vingt-et-un","correct":False},{"id":"d","text":"soixante-trente-un","correct":False}]},
      {"type":"fill-blank","text":"73 = soixante-___","answers":["treize"]},
